        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Peel</strong> and slice the red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;finely</p> <p><strong>Place</strong> the onion in a sieve and (over a sink) pour all of the boiled water over them</p> <p><strong>Place </strong>them&nbsp;in a bowl and add the vinegar with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span>&nbsp;sugar and mix well</p> <p><strong>Leave</strong> to soak- this mellows the flavour</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/tuscan-panzanella-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile,</strong> tear the ciabatta into bite-size pieces</p> <p><strong>Add </strong>them to&nbsp;a baking tray and drizzle with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;olive oil</p> <p><strong>Season</strong> generously with salt and pepper</p> <p><strong>Place</strong> under the grill for 10 min or until crispy and browned</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/tuscan-panzanella-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, chop the cherry tomatoes in half</p> <p><strong>Chop</strong> the black olives coarsely</p> <p><strong>Place</strong> the tomatoes, olives, capers and oregano in a salad bowl</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/tuscan-panzanella-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Tear</strong> the basil and add to the salad bowl</p> <p><strong>Drain</strong> the mozzarella and tear it into bite-size pieces</p> <p><strong>Add</strong> to the salad bowl</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/tuscan-panzanella-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Drain</strong> the onion and discard the excess liquid</p> <p><strong>Add</strong>&nbsp;the onion to the salad bowl</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/tuscan-panzanella-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the toasted ciabatta and mix well</p> <p><strong>Season</strong> generously with pepper</p>",
